44size_t File__Analyze::Stream_Prepare (stream_t KindOfStream, size_t StreamPos)
45{
46 //Integrity
47 if (!Status[IsAccepted] || KindOfStream>Stream_Max)
48 return Error;
49
50 //Clear
51 if (KindOfStream==Stream_Max)
52 {
53 StreamKind_Last=Stream_Max;
54 StreamPos_Last=(size_t)-1;
55 return 0;
56 }
57
58 if (StreamPos>=Count_Get(KindOfStream))
59 {
60 //Add a stream
61 (*Stream)[KindOfStream].resize((*Stream)[KindOfStream].size()+1);
62 (*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].resize((*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].size()+1);
63 StreamKind_Last=KindOfStream;
64 StreamPos_Last=(*Stream)[KindOfStream].size()-1;
65 }
66 else
67 {
68 //Insert a stream
69 (*Stream)[KindOfStream].insert((*Stream)[KindOfStream].begin()+StreamPos, ZtringList());
70 (*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].insert((*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].begin()+StreamPos, ZtringListList());
71 StreamKind_Last=KindOfStream;
72 StreamPos_Last=StreamPos;
73 }
74
75 //Filling basic info
76 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, (size_t)General_Count, Count_Get(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last));
77 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_StreamKind, MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind_Last).Read(General_StreamKind, Info_Text));
78 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_StreamKind_String, MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind_Last).Read(General_StreamKind, Info_Text)), true);
79 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(KindOfStream); Pos++)
80 {
81 Fill(StreamKind_Last, Pos, General_StreamCount, Count_Get(StreamKind_Last), 10, true);
82 Fill(StreamKind_Last, Pos, General_StreamKindID, Pos, 10, true);
83 if (Count_Get(StreamKind_Last)>1)
84 Fill(StreamKind_Last, Pos, General_StreamKindPos, Pos+1, 10, true);
85 else
86 Clear(StreamKind_Last, Pos, General_StreamKindPos);
87 }
88
89 //Filling Lists & Counts
90 if (!IsSub && KindOfStream!=Stream_General)
91 {
92 const Ztring& StreamKind_Text=Get(KindOfStream, 0, General_StreamKind, Info_Text);
93 if (Count_Get(KindOfStream)>1)
94 {
95 ZtringList Temp; Temp.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
96 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Codec_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
97 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
98 Temp.insert(Temp.begin()+StreamPos, Ztring());
99 else
100 Temp.push_back(Ztring());
101 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Codec_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
102 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Language_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
103 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
104 Temp.insert(Temp.begin()+StreamPos, Ztring());
105 else
106 Temp.push_back(Ztring());
107 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Language_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
108 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
109 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
110 Temp.insert(Temp.begin()+StreamPos, Ztring());
111 else
112 Temp.push_back(Ztring());
113 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
114 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_WithHint_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
115 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
116 Temp.insert(Temp.begin()+StreamPos, Ztring());
117 else
118 Temp.push_back(Ztring());
119 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_WithHint_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
120 }
121
122 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("Count")).To_Local().c_str(), Count_Get(KindOfStream), 10, true);
123 }
124
125 //File name and dates
126 if (!IsSub && KindOfStream==Stream_General && File_Name.size()>0)
127 {
128 //File name
129 if (File_Name.find(__T("://"))==string::npos)
130 {
131 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_CompleteName, File_Name);
132 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FolderName, FileName::Path_Get(File_Name));
133 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileName, FileName::Name_Get(File_Name));
134 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileExtension, FileName::Extension_Get(File_Name));
135 }
136 else
137 {
138 Ztring FileName_Modified=File_Name;
139 size_t Begin=FileName_Modified.find(__T(':'), 6);
140 size_t End=FileName_Modified.find(__T('@'));
141 if (Begin!=string::npos && End!=string::npos && Begin<End)
142 FileName_Modified.erase(Begin, End-Begin);
143 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_CompleteName, FileName_Modified);
144 size_t FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset=FileName_Modified.find_last_of(__T('/'));
145 if (FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset!=string::npos)
146 {
147 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FolderName, FileName_Modified.substr(0, FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset));
148 size_t FileName_Modified_ExtensionSeparatorOffset=FileName_Modified.find_last_of(__T('.'));
149 if (FileName_Modified_ExtensionSeparatorOffset!=string::npos && FileName_Modified_ExtensionSeparatorOffset>FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset)
150 {
151 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileName, FileName_Modified.substr(FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset+1, FileName_Modified_ExtensionSeparatorOffset-(FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset+1)));
152 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileExtension, FileName_Modified.substr(FileName_Modified_ExtensionSeparatorOffset+1));
153 }
154 else
155 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileName, FileName_Modified.substr(FileName_Modified_PathSeparatorOffset+1));
156 }
157 }
158
159 //File dates
160 File F(File_Name);
161 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_File_Created_Date, F.Created_Get());
162 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_File_Created_Date_Local, F.Created_Local_Get());
163 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_File_Modified_Date, F.Modified_Get());
164 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_File_Modified_Date_Local, F.Modified_Local_Get());
165 }
166
167 //File size
168 if (((!IsSub || !File_Name.empty()) && KindOfStream==Stream_General && File_Size!=(int64u)-1))
169 Fill (Stream_General, 0, General_FileSize, File_Size);
170
171 //Fill with already ready data
172 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Fill_Temp.size(); Pos++)
173 if (Fill_Temp(Pos, 0).IsNumber())
174 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Temp(Pos, 0).To_int32u(), Fill_Temp(Pos, 1));
175 else
176 {
177 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Temp(Pos, 0).To_UTF8().c_str(), Fill_Temp(Pos, 1));
178 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
179 if (!Retrieve(KindOfStream, StreamPos_Last, "Demux_InitBytes").empty())
180 (*Stream_More)[KindOfStream][StreamPos_Last](Ztring().From_Local("Demux_InitBytes"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT"); //TODO: find a better way to hide additional fields by default
181 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
182 }
183 Fill_Temp.clear();
184
185 return StreamPos_Last; //The position in the stream count
186}
187
188size_t File__Analyze::Stream_Erase (stream_t KindOfStream, size_t StreamPos)
189{
190 //Integrity
191 if (!Status[IsAccepted] || KindOfStream>Stream_Max || StreamPos>=Count_Get(KindOfStream))
192 return Error;
193
194 //Filling Lists & Counts
195 if (!IsSub && KindOfStream!=Stream_General)
196 {
197 const Ztring& StreamKind_Text=Get(KindOfStream, 0, General_StreamKind, Info_Text);
198 ZtringList Temp; Temp.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
199 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Codec_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
200 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
201 Temp.erase(Temp.begin()+StreamPos);
202 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Codec_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
203 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Language_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
204 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
205 Temp.erase(Temp.begin()+StreamPos);
206 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Language_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
207 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
208 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
209 Temp.erase(Temp.begin()+StreamPos);
210 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
211 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_WithHint_List")).To_Local().c_str()));
212 if (StreamPos<Temp.size())
213 Temp.erase(Temp.begin()+StreamPos);
214 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_WithHint_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp.Read(), true);
215
216 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("Count")).To_Local().c_str(), Count_Get(KindOfStream)-1, 10, true);
217 }
218
219 //Insert a stream
220 (*Stream)[KindOfStream].erase((*Stream)[KindOfStream].begin()+StreamPos);
221 (*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].erase((*Stream_More)[KindOfStream].begin()+StreamPos);
222
223 //Filling basic info
224 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(KindOfStream); Pos++)
225 {
226 Fill(KindOfStream, Pos, General_StreamCount, Count_Get(StreamKind_Last), 10, true);
227 Fill(KindOfStream, Pos, General_StreamKindID, Pos, 10, true);
228 if (Count_Get(KindOfStream)>1)
229 Fill(KindOfStream, Pos, General_StreamKindPos, Pos+1, 10, true);
230 else
231 Clear(KindOfStream, Pos, General_StreamKindPos);
232 }
233
234 StreamKind_Last=Stream_Max;
235 StreamPos_Last=(size_t)-1;
236
237 return (*Stream)[KindOfStream].size()-1; //The position in the stream count
238}

241//***************************************************************************
242// Filling
243//***************************************************************************
244
245//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
246void File__Analyze::Fill (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter, const Ztring &Value, bool Replace)
247{
248 //MergedStreams
249 if (FillAllMergedStreams)
250 {
251 FillAllMergedStreams=false;
252 size_t s = MergedStreams_Last.size();
253 for (size_t i=0; i<s; ++i)
254 Fill(MergedStreams_Last[i].StreamKind, MergedStreams_Last[i].StreamPos, Parameter, Value, Replace);
255 FillAllMergedStreams=true;
256 return;
257 }
258
259 //Integrity
260 if (!Status[IsAccepted] || StreamKind>Stream_Max || Parameter==(size_t)-1)
261 return;
262
263 //Handle Value before StreamKind
264 if (StreamKind==Stream_Max || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size())
265 {
266 ZtringList NewList;
267 NewList.push_back(Ztring().From_Number(Parameter));
268 NewList.push_back(Value);
269 Fill_Temp.push_back(NewList);
270 return; //No streams
271 }
272
273 //Some defaults
274 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Commercial))
275 Replace=true;
276 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Commercial_IfAny))
277 Replace=true;
278
279 if (!Replace && Value.empty())
280 return;
281 if (Replace && Value.empty())
282 {
283 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter);
284 return;
285 }
286
287 Ztring &Target=(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter);
288 if (Target.empty() || Replace)
289 Target=Value; //First value
290 else
291 {
292 Target+=MediaInfoLib::Config.TagSeparator_Get();
293 Target+=Value;
294 }
295 Status[IsUpdated]=true;
296
297 //Deprecated
298 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_BitDepth))
299 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Resolution), Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_BitDepth)), true);
300 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && Parameter==Video_Colorimetry)
301 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_ChromaSubsampling, Value, Replace);
302
303 switch (StreamKind)
304 {
305 case Stream_Video:
306 switch (Parameter)
307 {
308 case Video_Width: if (IsRawStream) Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Sampled_Width, Value); break;
309 case Video_Height: if (IsRawStream) Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Sampled_Height, Value); break;
310 case Video_DisplayAspectRatio: DisplayAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width, Video_Height, Video_PixelAspectRatio, Video_DisplayAspectRatio); break;
311 case Video_PixelAspectRatio: PixelAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width, Video_Height, Video_PixelAspectRatio, Video_DisplayAspectRatio); break;
312 case Video_DisplayAspectRatio_CleanAperture: DisplayAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width_CleanAperture, Video_Height_CleanAperture, Video_PixelAspectRatio_CleanAperture, Video_DisplayAspectRatio_CleanAperture); break;
313 case Video_PixelAspectRatio_CleanAperture: PixelAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width_CleanAperture, Video_Height_CleanAperture, Video_PixelAspectRatio_CleanAperture, Video_DisplayAspectRatio_CleanAperture); break;
314 case Video_DisplayAspectRatio_Original: DisplayAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width_Original, Video_Height_Original, Video_PixelAspectRatio_Original, Video_DisplayAspectRatio_Original); break;
315 case Video_PixelAspectRatio_Original: PixelAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width_Original, Video_Height_Original, Video_PixelAspectRatio_Original, Video_DisplayAspectRatio_Original); break;
316 }
317 break;
318 case Stream_Audio:
319 switch (Parameter)
320 {
321 case Audio_SamplesPerFrame:
322 if (Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_FrameRate).empty())
323 {
324 float64 SamplesPerFrame=Value.To_float64();
325 float64 SamplingRate=DBL_MAX;
326 ZtringList SamplingRates;
327 SamplingRates.Separator_Set(0, " / ");
328 SamplingRates.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_SamplingRate));
329 if (!SamplingRates.empty())
330 {
331 size_t i=SamplingRates.size();
332 do
333 {
334 --i;
335 float64 SamplingRateTemp = SamplingRates[i].To_float64();
336 if (SamplingRateTemp && SamplingRateTemp<SamplingRate)
337 SamplingRate=SamplingRateTemp; // Using the lowest valid one (e.g. AAC doubles sampling rate but the legacy sampling rate is the real frame)
338 }
339 while (i);
340 }
341 if (SamplesPerFrame && SamplingRate && SamplingRate!=DBL_MAX && SamplesPerFrame!=SamplingRate)
342 {
343 float64 FrameRate=SamplingRate/SamplesPerFrame;
344 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_FrameRate, FrameRate);
345 }
346 }
347 }
348 break;
349 case Stream_Image:
350 switch (Parameter)
351 {
352 case Image_DisplayAspectRatio: DisplayAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Image, StreamPos, Image_Width, Image_Height, Image_PixelAspectRatio, Image_DisplayAspectRatio); break;
353 case Image_PixelAspectRatio: PixelAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Image, StreamPos, Image_Width, Image_Height, Image_PixelAspectRatio, Image_DisplayAspectRatio); break;
354 case Image_DisplayAspectRatio_Original: DisplayAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Image, StreamPos, Image_Width_Original, Image_Height_Original, Image_PixelAspectRatio_Original, Image_DisplayAspectRatio_Original); break;
355 case Image_PixelAspectRatio_Original: PixelAspectRatio_Fill(Value, Stream_Image, StreamPos, Image_Width_Original, Image_Height_Original, Image_PixelAspectRatio_Original, Image_DisplayAspectRatio_Original); break;
356 }
357 break;
358 default:
359 // TODO;
360 break;
361 }
362
363 //Commercial name
364 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format))
365 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Commercial), Value);
366 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Commercial_IfAny))
367 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Commercial), Value, true);
368
369 if (!IsSub)
370 {
371 Ztring ParameterName=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter, Info_Name);
372
373 //Lists
374 if (StreamKind!=Stream_General && (ParameterName==__T("Codec/String")
375 || ParameterName==__T("Language/String")
376 || ParameterName==__T("Format")
377 || ParameterName==__T("CodecID/Hint")))
378 {
379 Ztring Temp1, Temp2;
380 for (size_t StreamPos_Local=0; StreamPos_Local<(*Stream)[StreamKind].size(); StreamPos_Local++)
381 {
382 if (ParameterName==__T("CodecID/Hint"))
383 Temp1+=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_Local, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format))+__T(" / ");
384 else
385 Temp1+=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_Local, Parameter)+__T(" / ");
386 if (ParameterName==__T("Format")
387 || ParameterName==__T("CodecID/Hint"))
388 {
389 Temp2+=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_Local, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format));
390 if (!Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_Local, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_CodecID_Hint)).empty())
391 {
392 Temp2+=__T(" (");
393 Temp2+=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_Local, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_CodecID_Hint));
394 Temp2+=__T(")");
395 }
396 Temp2+=__T(" / ");
397 }
398 }
399 if (!Temp1.empty())
400 Temp1.resize(Temp1.size()-3); //Delete extra " / "
401 if (!Temp2.empty())
402 Temp2.resize(Temp2.size()-3); //Delete extra " / "
403 Ztring StreamKind_Text=Get(StreamKind, 0, General_StreamKind, Info_Text);
404 if (ParameterName==__T("Codec/String"))
405 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Codec_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp1, true);
406 if (ParameterName==__T("Language/String"))
407 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Language_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp1, true);
408 if (ParameterName==__T("Format")
409 || ParameterName==__T("CodecID/Hint"))
410 {
411 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp1, true);
412 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Ztring(StreamKind_Text+__T("_Format_WithHint_List")).To_Local().c_str(), Temp2, true);
413 }
414 }
415
416 //General Format
417 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format) && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Format).empty() && !Value.empty())
418 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format, Value); //If not already filled, we are filling with the stream format
419
420 //ID
421 if (Parameter==General_ID)
422 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID_String, Value, Replace);
423
424 //Format
425 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format))
426 {
427 if ((Replace && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Info).empty()) || Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Info)).empty())
428 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Info), MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Info), true);
429 if ((Replace && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Url).empty()) || Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Url)).empty())
430 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format_Url) , MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Url), true);
431 if (StreamKind!=Stream_Menu)
432 {
433 if ((Replace && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_InternetMediaType).empty()) || Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_InternetMediaType)).empty())
434 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_InternetMediaType), MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_InternetMediaType), true);
435 if ((Replace && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Compression_Mode).empty()) || Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Compression_Mode)).empty())
436 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Compression_Mode), MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Format)), InfoFormat_Compression_Mode), true);
437 }
438 if (StreamKind==Stream_General)
439 {
440 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format_Extensions, MediaInfoLib::Config.Format_Get(Value, InfoFormat_Extensions), true);
441 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format_String, Value, true);
442 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Codec, Value, true);
443 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Codec_String, Value, true);
444 }
445 }
446 if (StreamKind==Stream_General && Parameter==General_Format_Info)
447 (*Stream)[Stream_General][0](General_Codec_Info)=Value;
448 if (StreamKind==Stream_General && Parameter==General_Format_Url)
449 (*Stream)[Stream_General][0](General_Codec_Url)=Value;
450 if (StreamKind==Stream_General && Parameter==General_Format_Extensions)
451 (*Stream)[Stream_General][0](General_Codec_Extensions)=Value;
452 if (StreamKind==Stream_General && Parameter==General_Format_Settings)
453 (*Stream)[Stream_General][0](General_Codec_Settings)=Value;
454
455 //Codec
456 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec) && MediaInfoLib::Config.Legacy_Get())
457 {
458 const Ztring &C1=MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec)), InfoCodec_Name, (stream_t)StreamKind);
459 if (C1.empty())
460 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec_String), Value, true);
461 else
462 {
463 Ztring D=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "Codec/Family");
464 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec_String), C1, true);
465 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, "Codec/Family", MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec)), InfoCodec_KindofCodec, StreamKind), true);
466 Ztring B=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec));
467 Ztring C=MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(B, InfoCodec_KindofCodec, StreamKind);
468 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec_Info) , MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec)), InfoCodec_Description, StreamKind), true);
469 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec_Url) , MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Codec)), InfoCodec_Url, StreamKind), true);
470 }
471 }
472
473 //CodecID_Description
474 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_CodecID_Info) && Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_CodecID_Description))==Value)
475 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_CodecID_Description));
476
477 //BitRate from BitRate_Nominal
478 if ((Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_BitRate)
479 || Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_BitRate_Nominal))
480 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
481 && Config->File_MergeBitRateInfo_Get()
482 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
483 )
484 {
485 float32 BitRate=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate").To_float32();
486 float32 BitRate_Nominal=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate_Nominal").To_float32();
487 if (BitRate_Nominal>BitRate*0.95 && BitRate_Nominal<BitRate*1.05)
488 {

490 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate_Nominal");
491 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate", Temp, true);
492 }

497 || Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_BitRate_Maximum))
498 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
499 && Config->File_MergeBitRateInfo_Get()
500 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
501 )
502 {
503 float32 BitRate=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate").To_float32();
504 float32 BitRate_Maximum=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate_Maximum").To_float32();
505 if (BitRate>BitRate_Maximum*0.99 && BitRate<BitRate_Maximum*1.01)
506 {
507 Ztring Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate_Maximum");
508 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate_Maximum");
509 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, "BitRate", Temp, true);

514 if (StreamKind==Stream_General && Parameter==General_FileSize)

518 for (size_t Kind=Stream_Video; Kind<Stream_Menu; Kind++)
519 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get((stream_t)Kind); Pos++)
520 FileSize_FileSize123((stream_t)Kind, Pos, Fill_Parameter((stream_t)Kind, Generic_StreamSize));

524 //Delay/Video
525 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && StreamPos==0 && Parameter==Video_Delay)
526 {

528 if (!Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Delay).empty())
529 {
530 Fill(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Video_Delay, Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Delay).To_int64s()-Value.To_int64s(), 10, true);
531 if (Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Video_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
532 for (size_t Param_Pos=Audio_Video_Delay+1; Param_Pos<=Audio_Video_Delay+4; Param_Pos++)

535 }
536 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Text); Pos++)
537 if (!Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Delay).empty())
538 {
539 Fill(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Video_Delay, Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Delay).To_int64s()-Value.To_int64s(), 10, true);
540 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Video_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
541 for (size_t Param_Pos=Text_Video_Delay+1; Param_Pos<=Text_Video_Delay+4; Param_Pos++)
542 if (Param_Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Text][Pos].size())
543 (*Stream)[Stream_Text][Pos][Param_Pos].clear();
544 }
545 }
546 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio && Parameter==Audio_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
547 {
548 if (Replace)
549 Clear(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Video_Delay);
550 ZtringList AudioDelay; AudioDelay.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / ")); AudioDelay.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Delay));

555 if (VideoDelay.size()==1 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Video_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
556 for (size_t Pos=Audio_Video_Delay+1; Pos<=Audio_Video_Delay+4; Pos++)
557 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos].size())
558 (*Stream)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
559 }
560 }
561 if (StreamKind==Stream_Text && Parameter==Text_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
562 {
563 Ztring MuxingMode_MoreInfo=Get(Stream_Text, StreamPos, "MuxingMode_MoreInfo");
564 Ztring StreamID=MuxingMode_MoreInfo.SubString(__T("Muxed in Video #"), Ztring());

566 if (StreamID_Int)
567 StreamID_Int--;
568 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Video_Delay, Value.To_int64s()-Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamID_Int, Video_Delay).To_int64s(), 10, true);
569 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Video_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
570 for (size_t Pos=Text_Video_Delay+1; Pos<=Text_Video_Delay+4; Pos++)
571 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Text][StreamPos].size())
572 (*Stream)[Stream_Text][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
573 }
574 if (StreamKind==Stream_Other && Parameter==Other_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Other_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
575 {
576 if (Replace)
577 Clear(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Other_Video_Delay);
578 ZtringList OtherDelay; OtherDelay.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / ")); OtherDelay.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Other_Delay));
579 ZtringList VideoDelay; VideoDelay.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / ")); VideoDelay.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay));
580 if (!OtherDelay.empty() && !VideoDelay.empty() && OtherDelay.size() <= VideoDelay.size())
581 {
582 Fill(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Other_Video_Delay, OtherDelay(OtherDelay.size()-1).To_int64s()-VideoDelay(VideoDelay.size()-1).To_int64s(), 10);
583 if (VideoDelay.size()==1 && Retrieve(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Other_Video_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
584 for (size_t Pos=Other_Video_Delay+1; Pos<=Other_Video_Delay+4; Pos++)
585 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Other][StreamPos].size())
586 (*Stream)[Stream_Other][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
587 }
588 }
589
590 //Delay/Video0
591 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && StreamPos==0 && Parameter==Video_Delay)
592 {
593 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Audio); Pos++)
594 if (!Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Delay).empty())
595 {
596 Fill(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Video0_Delay, Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Delay).To_int64s()-Value.To_int64s(), 10, true);
597 if (Retrieve(Stream_Audio, Pos, Audio_Video0_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
598 for (size_t Param_Pos=Audio_Video0_Delay+1; Param_Pos<=Audio_Video0_Delay+4; Param_Pos++)
599 if (Param_Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Audio][Pos].size())
600 (*Stream)[Stream_Audio][Pos][Param_Pos].clear();
601 }
602 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Text); Pos++)
603 if (!Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Delay).empty())
604 {
605 Fill(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Video0_Delay, Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Delay).To_int64s()-Value.To_int64s(), 10, true);
606 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_Video0_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
607 for (size_t Param_Pos=Text_Video0_Delay+1; Param_Pos<=Text_Video0_Delay+4; Param_Pos++)
608 if (Param_Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Text][Pos].size())
609 (*Stream)[Stream_Text][Pos][Param_Pos].clear();
610 }
611 }
612 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio && Parameter==Audio_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
613 {
614 if (Replace)
615 Clear(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Video0_Delay);
616 ZtringList AudioDelay; AudioDelay.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / ")); AudioDelay.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Delay));
617 ZtringList VideoDelay; VideoDelay.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / ")); VideoDelay.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay));
618 if (!AudioDelay.empty() && !VideoDelay.empty() && AudioDelay.size() <= VideoDelay.size())
619 {
620 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Video0_Delay, AudioDelay(AudioDelay.size() - 1).To_int64s() - VideoDelay(VideoDelay.size() - 1).To_int64s(), 10);
621 if (VideoDelay.size()==1 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Video0_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
622 for (size_t Pos=Audio_Video0_Delay+1; Pos<=Audio_Video0_Delay+4; Pos++)
623 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos].size())
624 (*Stream)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
625 }
626 }
627 if (StreamKind==Stream_Text && Parameter==Text_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
628 {
629 Ztring MuxingMode_MoreInfo=Get(Stream_Text, StreamPos, "MuxingMode_MoreInfo");
630 Ztring StreamID=MuxingMode_MoreInfo.SubString(__T("Muxed in Video #"), Ztring());
631 size_t StreamID_Int=(size_t)StreamID.To_int64u();
632 if (StreamID_Int)
633 StreamID_Int--;
634 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Video0_Delay, Value.To_int64s()-Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamID_Int, Video_Delay).To_int64s(), 10, true);
635 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, StreamPos, Text_Video0_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
636 for (size_t Pos=Text_Video0_Delay+1; Pos<=Text_Video0_Delay+4; Pos++)
637 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Text][StreamPos].size())
638 (*Stream)[Stream_Text][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
639 }
640 if (StreamKind==Stream_Other && Parameter==Text_Delay && Count_Get(Stream_Video) && !Retrieve(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Text_Delay).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Delay).empty())
641 {
642 Ztring MuxingMode_MoreInfo=Get(Stream_Other, StreamPos, "MuxingMode_MoreInfo");
643 Ztring StreamID=MuxingMode_MoreInfo.SubString(__T("Muxed in Video #"), Ztring());
644 size_t StreamID_Int=(size_t)StreamID.To_int64u();
645 if (StreamID_Int)
646 StreamID_Int--;
647 Fill(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Text_Video0_Delay, Value.To_int64s()-Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamID_Int, Video_Delay).To_int64s(), 10, true);
648 if (Retrieve(Stream_Other, StreamPos, Text_Video0_Delay).To_int64u()==0)
649 for (size_t Pos=Text_Video0_Delay+1; Pos<=Text_Video0_Delay+4; Pos++)
650 if (Pos<(*Stream)[Stream_Other][StreamPos].size())
651 (*Stream)[Stream_Other][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
652 }
653
654 //Language
655 //-Find 2-digit language
656 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Language))
657 {
658 //Removing old strings
659 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+1); //String
660 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+2); //String1
661 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+3); //String2
662 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+4); //String3
663 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+5); //String4
664
665 ZtringListList Languages;
666 Languages.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
667 Languages.Separator_Set(1, __T("-"));
668 Languages.Write((*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter]);
669
670 //Canonizing
671 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Languages.size(); Pos++)
672 {
673 Ztring Language_Orig;
674
675 //Removing undefined languages
676 if (Languages[Pos].size()>=1)
677 {
678 Language_Orig=Languages[Pos][0];
679 Languages[Pos][0].MakeLowerCase();
680 if ((Languages[Pos][0].size()==3 && (Languages[Pos][0]==__T("mis")
681 || Languages[Pos][0]==__T("und")
682 || Languages[Pos][0]==__T("???")
683 || Languages[Pos][0]==__T(" ")))
684 || (Languages[Pos][0].size()==2 && Languages[Pos][0]==__T(" ")))
685 Languages[Pos].clear();
686 }
687
688 //Finding ISO-639-1 from ISO-639-2 or translated name
689 if (Languages[Pos].size()>=1)
690 {
691 if (Languages[Pos][0].size()==3 && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_1_Get(Languages[Pos][0]).empty())
692 Languages[Pos][0]=MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_1_Get(Languages[Pos][0]);
693 if (Languages[Pos][0].size()>3 && !MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_Find(Languages[Pos][0]).empty())
694 Languages[Pos][0]=MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_Find(Languages[Pos][0]);
695 if (Languages[Pos][0].size()>3)
696 Languages[Pos][0]=Language_Orig; //We failed to detect language, using the original version
697 }
698 }
699
700 if (Languages.Read()!=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter))
701 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter, Languages.Read(), true);
702 else
703 {
704 ZtringList Language1; Language1.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
705 ZtringList Language2; Language2.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
706 ZtringList Language3; Language3.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
707 ZtringList Language4; Language4.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
708
709 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Languages.size(); Pos++)
710 {
711 if (Languages[Pos].size()>=1)
712 {
713 Ztring Language_Translated=MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("Language_")+Languages[Pos][0]);
714 if (Language_Translated.find(__T("Language_"))==0)
715 Language_Translated=Languages[Pos][0]; //No translation found
716 if (Languages[Pos].size()>=2)
717 {
718 if (Languages[Pos].size()==2 && Languages[Pos][1].size()>=2 && Languages[Pos][1].size()<=3 && (Languages[Pos][1][0]&0xDF)>=__T('A') && (Languages[Pos][1][0]&0xDF)<=__T('Z') && (Languages[Pos][1][1]&0xDF)>=__T('A') && (Languages[Pos][1][1]&0xDF)<=__T('Z'))
719 {
720 Language_Translated+=__T(" (");
721 Language_Translated+=Ztring(Languages[Pos][1]).MakeUpperCase();
722 Language_Translated+=__T(")");
723 }
724 else
725 for (size_t Pos2=1; Pos2<Languages[Pos].size(); Pos2++)
726 {
727 Language_Translated+=__T('-'); //As the original string
728 Language_Translated+=Languages[Pos][Pos2];
729 }
730 }
731 Language1.push_back(Language_Translated);
732 if (Languages[Pos][0].size()==2)
733 {
734 Language2.push_back(Languages[Pos][0]);
735 Language4.push_back(Languages[Pos].Read());
736 }
737 else
738 {
739 Language2.push_back(Ztring());
740 Language4.push_back(Ztring());
741 }
742 if (Languages[Pos][0].size()==3)
743 Language3.push_back(Languages[Pos][0]);
744 else if (!MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_2_Get(Languages[Pos][0]).empty())
745 Language3.push_back(MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_2_Get(Languages[Pos][0]));
746 else
747 Language3.push_back(Ztring());
748 }
749 else
750 {
751 Language1.push_back(Ztring());
752 Language2.push_back(Ztring());
753 Language3.push_back(Ztring());
754 Language4.push_back(Ztring());
755 }
756 }
757
758 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+2, Language1.Read()); //String1
759 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+3, Language2.Read()); //String2
760 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+4, Language3.Read()); //String3
761 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+5, Language4.Read()); //String4
762 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+1, Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+2)); //String
763 }
764 }
765
766 //ServiceName / ServiceProvider
767 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_ServiceName)
768 || Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_ServiceProvider))
769 {
770 if (Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter).find(__T(" - "))==string::npos && (Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter).find(__T(":"))==2 || Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter).find(__T(":"))==3))
771 {
772 Ztring Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter);
773 Temp.erase(0, Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter).find(__T(":"))+1);
774 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter)=Temp;
775 }
776 }
777
778 //FrameRate Nominal
779 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && (Parameter==Video_FrameRate || Parameter==Video_FrameRate_Nominal))
780 {
781 float32 FrameRate=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate).To_float32();
782 float32 FrameRate_Nominal=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Nominal).To_float32();
783 if (FrameRate_Nominal>FrameRate*0.9995 && FrameRate_Nominal<FrameRate*1.0005)
784 {
785 Ztring Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Nominal);
786 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Nominal);
787 if (Parameter==Video_FrameRate)
788 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter, Temp, true);
789 }
790 }
791
792 //Well known framerate values
793 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && (Parameter==Video_FrameRate || Parameter==Video_FrameRate_Nominal || Parameter==Video_FrameRate_Original)
794 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Original_Num).empty()) // Ignoring when there is a num/den with discrepency between container and raw stream
795 {
796 Video_FrameRate_Rounding(StreamPos, (video)Parameter);
797 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Nominal)==Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate))
798 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Nominal);
799 if (Parameter!=Video_FrameRate_Original && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Original)==Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate))
800 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Original);
801 }
802
803 //Bits/(Pixel*Frame)
804 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && (Parameter==Video_BitRate || Parameter==Video_BitRate_Nominal || Parameter==Video_Width || Parameter==Video_Height || Parameter==Video_FrameRate))
805 {
806 float32 BitRate=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_BitRate).To_float32();
807 if (BitRate==0)
808 BitRate=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_BitRate_Nominal).To_float32();
809 float F1=(float)Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Width).To_int32s()*(float)Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Height).To_int32s()*Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate).To_float32();
810 if (BitRate && F1)
811 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Bits__Pixel_Frame_, BitRate/F1, 3, true);
812 }
813
814 //Special audio cases
815 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio && Parameter==Audio_CodecID
816 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Channel_s_).empty()
817 &&(Value==__T("samr")
818 || Value==__T("sawb")
819 || Value==__T("7A21")
820 || Value==__T("7A22"))
821 )
822 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Channel_s_, 1, 10, true); //AMR is always with 1 channel
823
824 //Well known bitrate values
825 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && (Parameter==Video_BitRate || Parameter==Video_BitRate_Nominal))
826 Video_BitRate_Rounding(StreamPos, (video)Parameter);
827 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio && (Parameter==Audio_BitRate || Parameter==Audio_BitRate_Nominal))
828 Audio_BitRate_Rounding(StreamPos, (audio)Parameter);
829 }
830}

832//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
833void File__Analyze::Fill (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter, float32 Value, int8u AfterComma, bool Replace)
834{
835 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video && Parameter==Video_FrameRate)
836 {
837 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Num);
838 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Den);
839
840 if (Value)
841 {
842 if (float32_int32s(Value) - Value*1.001000 > -0.000002
843 && float32_int32s(Value) - Value*1.001000 < +0.000002) // Detection of precise 1.001 (e.g. 24000/1001) taking into account precision of 32-bit float
844 {
845 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Num, Value*1001, 0, Replace);
846 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Den, 1001, 10, Replace);
847 }
848 if (float32_int32s(Value) - Value*1.001001 > -0.000002
849 && float32_int32s(Value) - Value*1.001001 < +0.000002) // Detection of rounded 1.001 (e.g. 23976/1000) taking into account precision of 32-bit float
850 {
851 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Num, Value*1000, 0, Replace);
852 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Video_FrameRate_Den, 1000, 10, Replace);
853 }
854 }
855 }
856
857 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter, Ztring::ToZtring(Value, AfterComma), Replace);
858}
859
860//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
861void File__Analyze::Fill (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, const char* Parameter, const Ztring &Value, bool Replace)
862{
863 //Integrity
864 if (!Status[IsAccepted] || StreamKind>Stream_Max || Parameter==NULL || Parameter[0]=='\0')
865 return;
866
867 //Handle Value before StreamKind
868 if (StreamKind==Stream_Max || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size())
869 {
870 Ztring ParameterZ=Ztring().From_UTF8(Parameter);
871 if (Replace)
872 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Fill_Temp.size(); Pos++)
873 if (Fill_Temp[Pos](0)==ParameterZ)
874 {
875 Fill_Temp.erase(Fill_Temp.begin()+Pos);
876 Pos--;
877 }
878 ZtringList NewList;
879 NewList.push_back(ParameterZ);
880 NewList.push_back(Value);
881 Fill_Temp.push_back(NewList);
882 return; //No streams
883 }
884
885 //Handling of well known parameters
886 size_t Pos=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Find(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
887 if (Pos!=Error)
888 {
889 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Pos, Value, Replace);
890 return;
891 }
892
893 if (StreamKind==Stream_Other && !strcmp(Parameter, "Codec"))
894 return; // "Codec" does not exist in "Other"
895
896 //Handling of unknown parameters
897 if (Value.empty())
898 {
899 if (Replace)
900 {
901 size_t Pos_ToReplace=(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].Find(Ztring().From_ISO_8859_1(Parameter), Info_Name);
902 if (Pos_ToReplace!=(size_t)-1)
903 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].erase((*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].begin()+Pos_ToReplace); //Empty value --> remove the line
904 }
905 }
906 else
907 {
908 Ztring &Target=(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Ztring().From_ISO_8859_1(Parameter), Info_Text);
909 if (Target.empty() || Replace)
910 {
911 Target=Value; //First value
912 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Ztring().From_ISO_8859_1(Parameter), Info_Name_Text)=MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
913 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Ztring().From_ISO_8859_1(Parameter), Info_Options)=__T("Y NT");
914 }
915 else
916 {
917 Target+=MediaInfoLib::Config.TagSeparator_Get();
918 Target+=Value;
919 }
920 }
921 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, (size_t)General_Count, Count_Get(StreamKind, StreamPos), 10, true);
922}

924//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
925const Ztring &File__Analyze::Retrieve_Const (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter, info_t KindOfInfo)
926{
927 //Integrity
928 if (StreamKind>=Stream_Max
929 || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size()
930 || Parameter>=(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
931 return MediaInfoLib::Config.EmptyString_Get();
932
933 if (KindOfInfo!=Info_Text)
934 return MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind, Parameter, KindOfInfo);
935 return (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter);
936}

938//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
939Ztring File__Analyze::Retrieve (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter, info_t KindOfInfo)
940{
941 //Integrity
942 if (StreamKind>=Stream_Max
943 || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size()
944 || Parameter>=(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
945 return MediaInfoLib::Config.EmptyString_Get();
946
947 if (KindOfInfo!=Info_Text)
948 return MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind, Parameter, KindOfInfo);
949 return (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter);
950}

952//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
953const Ztring &File__Analyze::Retrieve_Const (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, const char* Parameter, info_t KindOfInfo)
954{
955 //Integrity
956 if (StreamKind>=Stream_Max
957 || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size()
958 || Parameter==NULL
959 || Parameter[0]=='\0')
960 return MediaInfoLib::Config.EmptyString_Get();
961
962 if (KindOfInfo!=Info_Text)
963 return MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind, Parameter, KindOfInfo);
964 size_t Parameter_Pos=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Find(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
965 if (Parameter_Pos==Error)
966 {
967 Parameter_Pos=(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].Find(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
968 if (Parameter_Pos==Error)
969 return MediaInfoLib::Config.EmptyString_Get();
970 return (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter_Pos, 1);
971 }
972 return (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter_Pos);
973}

998//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
999void File__Analyze::Clear (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, const char* Parameter)
1000{
1001 //Integrity
1002 if (StreamKind>=Stream_Max
1003 || Parameter==NULL
1004 || Parameter[0]=='\0')
1005 return;
1006
1007 if (StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size())
1008 {
1009 size_t Pos=Fill_Temp.Find(Ztring().From_UTF8(Parameter));
1010 if (Pos!=string::npos)
1011 Fill_Temp.erase(Fill_Temp.begin()+Pos);
1012 return;
1013 }
1014
1015 size_t Parameter_Pos=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Find(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
1016 if (Parameter_Pos==Error)
1017 {
1018 Parameter_Pos=(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].Find(Ztring().From_Local(Parameter));
1019 if (Parameter_Pos==Error)
1020 return;
1021 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos](Parameter_Pos, 1).clear();
1022 return;
1023 }
1024
1025 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter_Pos);
1026}

1028//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1029void File__Analyze::Clear (stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter)
1030{
1031 //Integrity
1032 if (StreamKind>=Stream_Max
1033 || StreamPos>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size())
1034 return;
1035
1036 //Normal
1037 if (Parameter<MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).size())
1038 {
1039 //Is something available?
1040 if (Parameter>=(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1041 return; //Was never filled, no nead to clear it
1042
1043 //Clearing
1044 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter].clear();
1045
1046 //Human readable
1047 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.ReadByHuman_Get())
1048 {
1049 //Strings
1050 const Ztring &List_Measure_Value=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Read(Parameter, Info_Measure);
1051 if (List_Measure_Value==__T(" byte"))
1052 {
1053 const Ztring &Temp=MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Read(Parameter, Info_Name);
1054 size_t List_Size=Temp.find(__T("StreamSize"))==string::npos?5:7; //for /String5, with percentage, and proportion
1055 for (size_t Pos=Parameter+1; Pos<=Parameter+List_Size; Pos++)
1056 if (Pos<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1057 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
1058 }
1059 else if (List_Measure_Value==__T(" bps") || List_Measure_Value==__T(" Hz"))
1060 {
1061 if (Parameter+1<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1062 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter+1].clear();
1063 }
1064 else if (List_Measure_Value==__T(" ms"))
1065 {
1066 for (size_t Pos=Parameter+1; Pos<=Parameter+6; Pos++)
1067 if (Pos<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1068 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Pos].clear();
1069 }
1070 else if (List_Measure_Value==__T("Yes"))
1071 {
1072 if (Parameter+1<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1073 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter+1].clear();
1074 }
1075 else if (!List_Measure_Value.empty())
1076 {
1077 if (Parameter+1<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1078 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter+1].clear();
1079 }
1080 else if (Parameter+1<(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size() && MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).Read(Parameter+1, Info_Name).find(__T("/String"))!=string::npos)
1081 {
1082 (*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos][Parameter+1].clear();
1083 }
1084 }
1085
1086 return;
1087 }
1088
1089 //More
1090 Parameter-=(*Stream)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size(); //For having Stream_More position
1091 if (Parameter<(*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].size())
1092 {
1093 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].erase((*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos].begin()+Parameter);
1094 return;
1095 }
1096}

1126//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1127size_t File__Analyze::Merge(MediaInfo_Internal &ToAdd, bool)
1128{
1129 size_t Count=0;
1130 for (size_t StreamKind=(size_t)Stream_General; StreamKind<(size_t)Stream_Max; StreamKind++)
1131 {
1132 size_t StreamPos_Count=ToAdd.Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind);
1133 for (size_t StreamPos=0; StreamPos<StreamPos_Count; StreamPos++)
1134 {
1135 //Prepare a new stream
1136 if (StreamPos>=Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind))
1137 Stream_Prepare((stream_t)StreamKind);
1138
1139 //Merge
1140 size_t Pos_Count=ToAdd.Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos);
1141 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Pos_Count; Pos++)
1142 {
1143 if (StreamKind!=Stream_General
1144 || !(Pos==General_CompleteName
1145 || Pos==General_FolderName
1146 || Pos==General_FileName
1147 || Pos==General_FileExtension
1148 || Pos==General_File_Created_Date
1149 || Pos==General_Format
1150 || Pos==General_Format_String
1151 || Pos==General_Format_Extensions
1152 || Pos==General_Format_Info
1153 || Pos==General_Codec
1154 || Pos==General_Codec_String
1155 || Pos==General_Codec_Extensions
1156 || Pos==General_FileSize
1157 || Pos==General_FileSize_String
1158 || Pos==General_FileSize_String1
1159 || Pos==General_FileSize_String2
1160 || Pos==General_FileSize_String3
1161 || Pos==General_FileSize_String4
1162 || Pos==General_File_Created_Date_Local
1163 || Pos==General_File_Modified_Date
1164 || Pos==General_File_Modified_Date_Local))
1165 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Ztring(ToAdd.Get((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Pos, Info_Name)).To_UTF8().c_str(), ToAdd.Get((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Pos), true);
1166 }
1167
1168 Count++;
1169 }
1170 }
1171
1172 return Count;
1173}

1175//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1176size_t File__Analyze::Merge(MediaInfo_Internal &ToAdd, stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos_From, size_t StreamPos_To, bool)
1177{
1178 size_t Pos_Count=ToAdd.Count_Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From);
1179 for (size_t Pos=General_Inform; Pos<Pos_Count; Pos++)
1180 if (!ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos).empty())
1181 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, Ztring(ToAdd.Get((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos, Info_Name)).To_UTF8().c_str(), ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos), true);
1182
1183 return 1;
1184}

1186//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1187size_t File__Analyze::Merge(File__Analyze &ToAdd, bool Erase)
1188{
1189 MergedStreams_Last.clear();
1190
1191 size_t Count=0;
1192 for (size_t StreamKind=(size_t)Stream_General+1; StreamKind<(size_t)Stream_Max; StreamKind++)
1193 for (size_t StreamPos=0; StreamPos<(*ToAdd.Stream)[StreamKind].size(); StreamPos++)
1194 {
1195 //Prepare a new stream
1196 Stream_Prepare((stream_t)StreamKind);
1197 MergedStreams_Last.push_back(streamidentity(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last));
1198
1199 //Merge
1200 Merge(ToAdd, (stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, StreamPos_Last, Erase);
1201
1202 Count++;
1203 }
1204 return Count;
1205}

1207//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1208size_t File__Analyze::Merge(File__Analyze &ToAdd, stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos_From, size_t StreamPos_To, bool Erase)
1209{
1210 //Integrity
1211 if (!Status[IsAccepted] || &ToAdd==NULL || StreamKind>=Stream_Max || !ToAdd.Stream || StreamPos_From>=(*ToAdd.Stream)[StreamKind].size())
1212 return 0;
1213
1214 //Destination
1215 while (StreamPos_To>=(*Stream)[StreamKind].size())
1216 Stream_Prepare(StreamKind);
1217
1218 //Specific stuff
1219 Ztring Width_Temp, Height_Temp, PixelAspectRatio_Temp, DisplayAspectRatio_Temp, FrameRate_Temp, FrameRate_Num_Temp, FrameRate_Den_Temp, FrameRate_Mode_Temp, ScanType_Temp, ScanOrder_Temp, Channels_Temp, Delay_Temp, Delay_DropFrame_Temp, Delay_Source_Temp, Delay_Settings_Temp, Source_Temp, Source_Kind_Temp, Source_Info_Temp;
1220 Ztring colour_description_present_Temp, colour_primaries_Temp, transfer_characteristics_Temp, matrix_coefficients_Temp;
1221 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video)
1222 {
1223 Width_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Width);
1224 Height_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Height);
1225 PixelAspectRatio_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_PixelAspectRatio); //We want to keep the PixelAspectRatio_Temp of the video stream
1226 DisplayAspectRatio_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_DisplayAspectRatio); //We want to keep the DisplayAspectRatio_Temp of the video stream
1227 FrameRate_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate); //We want to keep the FrameRate of AVI 120 fps
1228 FrameRate_Num_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Num);
1229 FrameRate_Den_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Den);
1230 FrameRate_Mode_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Mode); //We want to keep the FrameRate_Mode of AVI 120 fps
1231 ScanType_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType);
1232 ScanOrder_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder);
1233 colour_description_present_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present);
1234 if (!colour_description_present_Temp.empty())
1235 {
1236 colour_primaries_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries);
1237 transfer_characteristics_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics);
1238 matrix_coefficients_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients);
1239 }
1240 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present);
1241 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries);
1242 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics);
1243 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients);
1244 }
1245 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio)
1246 {
1247 Channels_Temp=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_Channel_s_);
1248 }
1249 if (ToAdd.Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Delay_Source))==__T("Container"))
1250 {
1251 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay"), true);
1252 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay");
1253 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_DropFrame", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_DropFrame"), true);
1254 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_DropFrame");
1255 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_Source", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source"), true);
1256 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source");
1257 if (!ToAdd.Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Format").empty()) //Exception: MPEG-4 TimeCode, settings are in the MPEG-4 header
1258 {
1259 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_Settings", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Settings"), true);
1260 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Settings");
1261 }
1262 }
1263 else
1264 {
1265 Delay_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay"); //We want to keep the Delay from the stream
1266 Delay_Settings_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Settings"); //We want to keep the Delay_Settings from the stream
1267 Delay_DropFrame_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_DropFrame"); //We want to keep the Delay_Source from the stream
1268 Delay_Source_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source"); //We want to keep the Delay_Source from the stream
1269 }
1270 Source_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source");
1271 Source_Kind_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Kind");
1272 Source_Info_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Info");
1273 Ztring BitRate_Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "BitRate");
1274
1275 //Merging
1276 size_t Count=0;
1277 size_t Size=ToAdd.Count_Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From);
1278 for (size_t Pos=General_Inform; Pos<Size; Pos++)
1279 {
1280 const Ztring &ToFill_Value=ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos);
1281 if (!ToFill_Value.empty() && (Erase || Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, Pos).empty()))
1282 {
1283 if (Pos<MediaInfoLib::Config.Info_Get(StreamKind).size())
1284 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, Pos, ToFill_Value, true);
1285 else
1286 {
1287 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos, Info_Name).To_UTF8().c_str(), ToFill_Value, true);
1288 (*Stream_More)[StreamKind][StreamPos_To](ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos, Info_Name), Info_Options)=ToAdd.Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_From, Pos, Info_Options);
1289 }
1290 Count++;
1291 }
1292 }
1293
1294 //Specific stuff
1295 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video)
1296 {
1297 Ztring PixelAspectRatio_Original=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_PixelAspectRatio);
1298 Ztring DisplayAspectRatio_Original=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_DisplayAspectRatio);
1299
1300 if (!Width_Temp.empty() && Width_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Width)
1301 && !(Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Format) == __T("DV") && Width_Temp == __T("1920") && (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Width) == __T("1280") || Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Width) == __T("1440")))) // Exception: DVCPRO HD is really 1440 but lot of containers fill the width value with the marketing width 1920, we ignore it
1302 {
1303 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Width_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_Width], true);
1304 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Width, Width_Temp, true);
1305 }
1306 if (!Height_Temp.empty() && Height_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Height))
1307 {
1308 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Height_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_Height], true);
1309 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_Height, Height_Temp, true);
1310 }
1311 if (!PixelAspectRatio_Temp.empty() && PixelAspectRatio_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_PixelAspectRatio))
1312 {
1313 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_PixelAspectRatio_Original, PixelAspectRatio_Original, true);
1314 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_PixelAspectRatio, PixelAspectRatio_Temp, true);
1315 }
1316 if (!DisplayAspectRatio_Temp.empty() && DisplayAspectRatio_Temp!=DisplayAspectRatio_Original)
1317 {
1318 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_DisplayAspectRatio_Original, DisplayAspectRatio_Original, true);
1319 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, DisplayAspectRatio_Temp, true);
1320 }
1321 if ((!FrameRate_Temp.empty() && FrameRate_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate))
1322 || (!FrameRate_Num_Temp.empty() && FrameRate_Num_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Num))
1323 || (!FrameRate_Den_Temp.empty() && FrameRate_Den_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Den)))
1324 {
1325 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Original, ToAdd.Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate), true);
1326 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Original_Num, ToAdd.Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Num), true);
1327 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Original_Den, ToAdd.Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Den), true);
1328 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate, FrameRate_Temp, true);
1329 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Num, FrameRate_Num_Temp, true);
1330 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Den, FrameRate_Den_Temp, true);
1331 }
1332 if (!FrameRate_Mode_Temp.empty() && FrameRate_Mode_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Mode))
1333 {
1334 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Mode_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_FrameRate_Mode], true);
1335 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_FrameRate_Mode, FrameRate_Mode_Temp, true);
1336 }
1337 if (!ScanType_Temp.empty() && (ScanType_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType) && !(ScanType_Temp==__T("Interlaced") && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType)==__T("MBAFF"))))
1338 {
1339 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_ScanType], true);
1340 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType, ScanType_Temp, true);
1341 }
1342 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType_Original)!=__T("Progressive") && ((!ScanOrder_Temp.empty() && ScanOrder_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder)) || !Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanType_Original).empty()))
1343 {
1344 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_ScanOrder], true);
1345 if (ScanOrder_Temp.empty())
1346 {
1347 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder);
1348 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder_String);
1349 }
1350 else
1351 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_ScanOrder, ScanOrder_Temp, true);
1352 }
1353 if (!colour_description_present_Temp.empty())
1354 {
1355 if (!colour_description_present_Temp.empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present).empty()
1356 && (colour_primaries_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries)
1357 || transfer_characteristics_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics)
1358 || matrix_coefficients_Temp!=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients)))
1359 {
1360 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_colour_description_present], true);
1361 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present, colour_description_present_Temp, true);
1362 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_colour_primaries], true);
1363 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries, colour_primaries_Temp, true);
1364 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_transfer_characteristics], true);
1365 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics, transfer_characteristics_Temp, true);
1366 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients_Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_To][Video_matrix_coefficients], true);
1367 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients, matrix_coefficients_Temp, true);
1368 }
1369 else
1370 {
1371 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_description_present, colour_description_present_Temp, true);
1372 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_colour_primaries, colour_primaries_Temp, true);
1373 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_transfer_characteristics, transfer_characteristics_Temp, true);
1374 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_To, Video_matrix_coefficients, matrix_coefficients_Temp, true);
1375 }
1376 }
1377 }
1378 if (StreamKind==Stream_Audio)
1379 {
1380 if (!Channels_Temp.empty())
1381 {
1382 //Test with legacy streams information
1383 bool IsOk=(Channels_Temp==Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_Channel_s_));
1384 if (!IsOk)
1385 {
1386 ZtringList Temp; Temp.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
1387 Temp.Write(Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_Channel_s_));
1388 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Temp.size(); Pos++)
1389 if (Channels_Temp==Temp[Pos])
1390 IsOk=true;
1391 }
1392
1393 //Special case with AES3: wrong container information is accepted
1394 if (!IsOk && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_MuxingMode).find(__T("SMPTE ST 337"))!=string::npos)
1395 IsOk=true;
1396
1397 if (!IsOk)
1398 {
1399 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_Channel_s__Original, (*Stream)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos_To][Audio_Channel_s_], true);
1400 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_To, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels_Temp, true);
1401 }
1402 }
1403 }
1404 if (!Delay_Source_Temp.empty() && Delay_Source_Temp!=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source"))
1405 {
1406 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay"), true);
1407 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay", Delay_Temp, true);
1408 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_Settings", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Settings"), true);
1409 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Settings", Delay_Settings_Temp, true);
1410 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_DropFrame", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_DropFrame"), true);
1411 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_DropFrame", Delay_DropFrame_Temp, true);
1412 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Original_Source", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source"), true);
1413 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Delay_Source", Delay_Source_Temp, true);
1414 }
1415 if (!Source_Temp.empty() && Source_Temp!=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source"))
1416 {
1417 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Original", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source"), true);
1418 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source", Source_Temp, true);
1419 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Original_Kind", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Kind"), true);
1420 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Kind", Source_Info_Temp, true);
1421 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Original_Info", Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Info"), true);
1422 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "Source_Info", Source_Info_Temp, true);
1423 }
1424 if (!BitRate_Temp.empty() && BitRate_Temp.find(__T(" / ")) == string::npos && Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "BitRate").find(__T("Unknown")) != string::npos)
1425 {
1426 Ztring Temp=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "BitRate");
1427 Temp.FindAndReplace(__T("Unknown"), BitRate_Temp, 0, Ztring_Recursive);
1428 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, "BitRate", Temp, true);
1429 }
1430
1431 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos_To, (size_t)General_Count, Count_Get(StreamKind, StreamPos_To), 10, true);
1432 return 1;
1433}

1636//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1637void File__Analyze::Tags()
1638{
1639 //Integrity
1640 if (!Count_Get(Stream_General))
1641 return;
1642
1643 //-Movie/Album
1644 if (!Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track).empty())
1645 {
1646 if (Count_Get(Stream_Video) && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Collection).empty())
1647 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Movie", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title));
1648 else
1649 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Track", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title));
1650 }
1651 if (!Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_More).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_More).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_More).empty())
1652 {
1653 if (Count_Get(Stream_Video) && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Collection).empty())
1654 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Movie_More", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_More));
1655 else
1656 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Track_More", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_More));
1657 }
1658 if (!Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_Url).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_Url).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_Url).empty())
1659 {
1660 if (Count_Get(Stream_Video) && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Collection).empty())
1661 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Movie/Url", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_Url));
1662 else
1663 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Track/Url", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_Url));
1664 }
1665 //-Title
1666 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie).empty())
1667 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie));
1668 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track).empty())
1669 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track));
1670 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_More).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_More).empty())
1671 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title_More", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_More));
1672 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_More).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_More).empty())
1673 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title_More", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_More));
1674 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_Url).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_Url).empty())
1675 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title/Url", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Movie_Url));
1676 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title_Url).empty() && !Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_Url).empty())
1677 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Title/Url", Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Track_Url));
1678
1679 //-Genre
1680 if (!Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre).empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre).size()<4 && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre)[0]>=__T('0') && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre)[0]<=__T('9'))
1681 {
1682 Ztring Genre;

1684 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre).size()==2) Genre=Ztring(__T("Genre_0" ))+Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre);
1685 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre).size()==3) Genre=Ztring(__T("Genre_" ))+Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Genre);
1686 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Genre", MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(Genre), true);
1687 }
1688}

1694//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1695//Duration
1696void File__Analyze::Duration_Duration123(stream_t StreamKind, size_t StreamPos, size_t Parameter)
1697{
1698 if (Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter).empty())
1699 return;
1700
1701 //Clearing old data
1702 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+1);
1703 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+2);
1704 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+3);
1705 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+4);
1706 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+5);
1707 Clear(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+6);
1708
1709 //Retrieving multiple values
1710 ZtringList List;
1711 List.Separator_Set(0, __T(" / "));
1712 List.Write(Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter));
1713
1714 //Per value
1715 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<List.size(); Pos++)
1716 {
1717 int32s HH, MM, Sec, MS;
1718 Ztring DurationString1, DurationString2, DurationString3;
1719 bool Negative=false;
1720 MS=List[Pos].To_int32s(); //in ms
1721
1722 if (MS<0)
1723 {
1724 Negative=true;
1725 MS=-MS;
1726 }
1727
1728 //Hours
1729 HH=MS/1000/60/60; //h
1730 if (HH>0)
1731 {
1732 DurationString1+=Ztring::ToZtring(HH)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("h"));
1733 DurationString2+=Ztring::ToZtring(HH)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("h"));
1734 if (HH<10)
1735 DurationString3+=Ztring(__T("0"))+Ztring::ToZtring(HH)+__T(":");
1736 else
1737 DurationString3+=Ztring::ToZtring(HH)+__T(":");
1738 MS-=HH*60*60*1000;
1739 }
1740 else
1741 {
1742 DurationString3+=__T("00:");
1743 }
1744
1745 //Minutes
1746 MM=MS/1000/60; //mn
1747 if (MM>0 || HH>0)
1748 {
1749 if (DurationString1.size()>0)
1750 DurationString1+=__T(" ");
1751 DurationString1+=Ztring::ToZtring(MM)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("mn"));
1752 if (DurationString2.size()<5)
1753 {
1754 if (DurationString2.size()>0)
1755 DurationString2+=__T(" ");
1756 DurationString2+=Ztring::ToZtring(MM)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("mn"));
1757 }
1758 if (MM<10)
1759 DurationString3+=Ztring(__T("0"))+Ztring::ToZtring(MM)+__T(":");
1760 else
1761 DurationString3+=Ztring::ToZtring(MM)+__T(":");
1762 MS-=MM*60*1000;
1763 }
1764 else
1765 {
1766 DurationString3+=__T("00:");
1767 }
1768
1769 //Seconds
1770 Sec=MS/1000; //s
1771 if (Sec>0 || MM>0 || HH>0)
1772 {
1773 if (DurationString1.size()>0)
1774 DurationString1+=__T(" ");
1775 DurationString1+=Ztring::ToZtring(Sec)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("s"));
1776 if (HH==0)
1777 {
1778 if (DurationString2.size()>0)
1779 DurationString2+=__T(" ");
1780 DurationString2+=Ztring::ToZtring(Sec)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("s"));
1781 }
1782 if (Sec<10)
1783 DurationString3+=Ztring(__T("0"))+Ztring::ToZtring(Sec)+__T(".");
1784 else
1785 DurationString3+=Ztring::ToZtring(Sec)+__T(".");
1786 MS-=Sec*1000;
1787 }
1788 else
1789 {
1790 DurationString3+=__T("00.");
1791 }
1792
1793 //Milliseconds
1794 if (MS>0 || Sec>0 || MM>0 || HH>0)
1795 {
1796 if (DurationString1.size()>0)
1797 DurationString1+=__T(" ");
1798 DurationString1+=Ztring::ToZtring(MS)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("ms"));
1799 if (HH==0 && MM==0)
1800 {
1801 if (DurationString2.size()>0)
1802 DurationString2+=__T(" ");
1803 DurationString2+=Ztring::ToZtring(MS)+MediaInfoLib::Config.Language_Get(__T("ms"));
1804 }
1805 if (MS<10)
1806 DurationString3+=Ztring(__T("00"))+Ztring::ToZtring(MS);
1807 else if (MS<100)
1808 DurationString3+=Ztring(__T("0"))+Ztring::ToZtring(MS);
1809 else
1810 DurationString3+=Ztring::ToZtring(MS);
1811 }
1812 else
1813 {
1814 DurationString3+=__T("000");
1815 }
1816
1817 if (Negative)
1818 {
1819 DurationString1=Ztring(__T("-"))+DurationString1;
1820 DurationString2=Ztring(__T("-"))+DurationString2;
1821 DurationString3=Ztring(__T("-"))+DurationString3;
1822 }
1823
1824 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+1, DurationString2); // /String
1825 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+2, DurationString1); // /String1
1826 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+3, DurationString2); // /String2
1827 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+4, DurationString3); // /String3
1828
1829 if (Parameter==Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_Duration))
1830 {
1831 Ztring DurationString4;
1832 Ztring FrameRateS=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_FrameRate));
1833 Ztring FrameCountS=Retrieve(StreamKind, StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind, Generic_FrameCount));
1834 if (!FrameRateS.empty() && !FrameCountS.empty() && FrameRateS.To_int64u() && FrameRateS.To_int64u()<256)
1835 {
1836 bool DropFrame=false;
1837 bool DropFrame_IsValid=false;
1838
1839 // Testing time code
1840 if (StreamKind==Stream_Video)
1841 {
1842 Ztring TC=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_TimeCode_FirstFrame);
1843 if (TC.size()>=11 && TC[2]==__T(':') && TC[5]==__T(':'))
1844 {
1845 switch (TC[8])
1846 {
1847 case __T(':'):
1848 DropFrame=false;
1849 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1850 break;
1851 case __T(';'):

1853 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1854 break;
1855 default : ;
1856 }
1857 }
1858 }

1865 {

1867 {
1868 case __T(':'):
1869 DropFrame=false;
1870 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1871 break;
1872 case __T(';'):
1873 DropFrame=true;
1874 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1875 break;
1876 default : ;
1877 }
1878 }
1879 }
1880
1881 // Testing time code track
1882 if (!DropFrame_IsValid)
1883 {
1884 for (size_t Step=Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Format)==__T("MXF")?0:1; Step<2; ++Step)
1885 {
1886 for (size_t TC_Pos=0; TC_Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Other); ++TC_Pos)
1887 if (Retrieve(Stream_Other, TC_Pos, Other_Type)==__T("Time code")
1888 && (Step || Retrieve(Stream_Other, TC_Pos, Other_TimeCode_Settings)==__T("Source Package")))
1889 {
1890 Ztring TC=Retrieve(Stream_Other, TC_Pos, Other_TimeCode_FirstFrame);
1891 if (TC.size()>=11 && TC[2]==__T(':') && TC[5]==__T(':'))
1892 {
1893 switch (TC[8])
1894 {
1895 case __T(':'):
1896 DropFrame=false;
1897 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1898 break;
1899 case __T(';'):
1900 DropFrame=true;
1901 DropFrame_IsValid=true;
1902 break;
1903 default : ;
1904 }
1905 }
1906
1907 if (DropFrame_IsValid)
1908 break; //Using first time code track
1909 }
1910
1911 if (DropFrame_IsValid)
1912 break; //Using first time code track
1913 }
1914 }
1915
1916 // Testing frame rate (1/1001)
1917 if (!DropFrame_IsValid)
1918 {
1919 float32 FrameRateF=FrameRateS.To_float32();
1920 int32s FrameRateI=float32_int32s(FrameRateS.To_float32());

1924 DropFrame=true;
1925 else
1926 DropFrame=false;
1927 }

1930 DurationString4.From_UTF8(TC.ToString());
1931
1932 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+5, DurationString4); // /String4
1933 }
1934 Ztring DurationString5(DurationString3);
1935 if (!DurationString4.empty())
1936 {
1937 DurationString5+=__T(' ');
1938 DurationString5+=__T('(');
1939 DurationString5+=DurationString4;
1940 DurationString5+=__T(')');
1941 }
1942 Fill(StreamKind, StreamPos, Parameter+6, DurationString5); // /String5
1943 }
